# Project Overview

Act as a senior team consisting of:

- Creative Director
- Senior UI/UX Designer
- Design System Architect
- WordPress/Template Design Expert
- Senior Frontend Engineer
- Accessibility Specialist
- Performance Engineer

The objective is NOT to redesign the website from scratch.

Instead, use the Univet template (https://univet.rstheme.com/blue/#) as the primary design foundation and evolve it into a premium institutional website for an Engineering College.

Maintain the overall structure, layout philosophy, spacing rhythm and navigation style of the template while significantly improving its visual quality, consistency and user experience.

The final website should feel like a modern international university rather than a generic education template.

---

# Design Inspiration

Take inspiration from:

- University of Oxford
- ETH Zürich
- Imperial College London
- Saarland University
- TU Delft
- EPFL
- MIT
- Apple
- Linear
- Stripe

Avoid startup aesthetics.

Avoid SaaS design language.

Avoid flashy marketing websites.

Prioritize credibility, clarity and academic excellence.

---

# Design Philosophy

The website should communicate:

- Trust
- Innovation
- Research
- Engineering Excellence
- Academic Prestige
- Professionalism

Every page should feel clean, structured and timeless.

---

# Template Guidelines

Keep the existing Univet section hierarchy wherever possible.

Reuse the existing component structure including:

- Hero
- Feature sections
- Statistics
- Department cards
- Faculty cards
- News
- Events
- Gallery
- CTA sections
- Footer

Improve the design rather than replacing it.

Do not introduce unnecessary layouts that deviate from the template.

---

# Visual Language

Style should be:

- Minimal
- Institutional
- Elegant
- Spacious
- Modern
- Editorial

Use generous whitespace.

Avoid clutter.

Maintain strong visual hierarchy.

Use consistent spacing throughout the website.

---

# Typography

Headings:
Source Serif 4

Body:
Source Sans 3

Code / Technical Sections:
IBM Plex Mono (optional)

Avoid:

- Poppins
- Montserrat
- Nunito
- Outfit
- Raleway
- Quicksand

---

# Color Palette

Primary:
#0F2744

Secondary:
#355070

Accent:
#B68C3A

Background:
#F7F8FA

Surface:
#EEF2F5

Text:
